{"tid":2451854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發...岩岩疑似撞鬼","createTime":"2021-03-18T11:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T11:44:52.000Z","uid":110997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0b9c927ca6a5c9ed8329ab9a3e9555c75c7ed5","tid":2451854,"uid":110997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的...我岩岩收工返屋企<br />\n去到樓下平台㩒密碼入lift <br />\n咁㩒密碼個地方就好鬼鼠既<br />\n需要經過一段小走廊行入去<br />\n入小走廊之前係大平台<br />\n<br />\n平台好多餐廳 岩岩都算多人流<br />\n但行入走廊基本上都係住客或者保安<br />\n果時得我一個only <br />\n<br />\n咁我由平台轉入走廊時已經聽到有人㩒密碼<br />\n聽到平時㩒密碼發出果d聲<br />\n果刻第一個想法係 有人㩒密碼 行快2步<br />\n唔洗自己㩒密碼<br />\n<br />\n但係聽到好似㩒左8下 差唔多<br />\n我樓下個密碼係4位數<br />\n我就估係咪條友㩒錯密碼<br />\n<br />\n點知我轉出走廊<br />\n仆你個街一個人都無<br />\n即刻打冷震打到上頭頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我㩒密碼時仲要㩒一下取消<br />\n再㩒一次先入到閘<br />\n9秒9衝返屋企<br />\n差d嚇到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家係廁所痾屎先諗返起<br />\n平台對出條街 平時7月d人就會係正對面化寶<br />\n又有人跳樓跳果個位死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知關唔關事<br />\n<br />\n屌好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d1746d68e272bc256ae7162ad4bc9f6fe2048d","tid":2451854,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJ3iMBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJ3iMBr.png&h=86d8e3d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4748e71b57244dd2ea48fbf9956dddd77d95f509","tid":2451854,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:41:23.000Z","msg":"啱啱同你經歷差唔多<br />\n又有少少唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係聽到第一次好似撳咗8下 差唔多<br />\n我樓下個密碼係4位數<br />\n我就估係咪條友撳錯密碼<br />\n<br />\n隔咗一陣又撳咗4下<br />\n再撳1下取消<br />\n又撳咗4下<br />\n<br />\n點知我轉出走廊<br />\n仆你個街一個人都無<br />\n即刻打冷震打到上頭頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我撳完密碼就9秒9衝返屋企<br />\n差啲嚇到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家係廁所痾屎先諗返起<br />\n平台對出條街 平時7月d人就會係正對面化寶<br />\n又有人跳樓跳果個位死過<br />\n唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1ee20725345d029bae65d47a5881dc581b9f9e","tid":2451854,"uid":61653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s7q5rBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs7q5rBQ.jpg&h=c43c6e88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed480904a4bf92960f1fa82883555115c7b8ce57","tid":2451854,"uid":56455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:42:01.000Z","msg":"都未到七月"},{"pid":"cbda0e804dfb92f2b23cb2bbb0a5c490e0cdc22f","tid":2451854,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母樓上臭濛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e46afdd90dcf66ca47f140c1317bde95b187735","tid":2451854,"uid":371330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d1746d68e272bc256ae7162ad4bc9f6fe2048d","tid":2451854,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJ3iMBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJ3iMBr.png&h=86d8e3d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"頂你！嚇親"},{"pid":"77b7fdb9c2c1da37182255035f20c2f477291621","tid":2451854,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d1746d68e272bc256ae7162ad4bc9f6fe2048d","tid":2451854,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJ3iMBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJ3iMBr.png&h=86d8e3d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"已射